name: Fly Free
description:
Opener on my 29th birthday

Protected in a cage, food is prepared, drinks never dry. But not with freedom, not being strong, instincts disappearing, there is no beauty.

After nearly two years of being a bird in a cage, at 29 this time, I want and will be a free bird. Back to doing photography activities that I started in 2012, which until now, I feel like I'm still young in the world of photography. It will continue to grow!
